                                    <div class="row solveText" style="display: block; padding:10px; color:#077307; overflow-x: auto; background-color: #d7f7d4;">
                                        <span style="color: black !important; font-weight: bold;">Solution:</span>
                                        <br />
                                        <span style="color: black !important;"><p class="pt-0000005188cdab-23a4-4691-a0bf-08bd12ee47ce" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml"><span class="math-tex" style="font-family: Cambria Math !important;" xmlns="">\({y}^{2}=4x⇒2y\frac{dy}{dx}=4⇒\frac{dy}{dx}=\frac{2}{y}\) </span><span xml:space="preserve" class="pt-0000015188cdab-23a4-4691-a0bf-08bd12ee47ce"> </span><style>span { white-space: pre-wrap; }p.pt-0000005188cdab-23a4-4691-a0bf-08bd12ee47ce {margin-right: 0.25in;text-align: left;line-height: 108%;margin-top: 0;margin-left: 0;margin-bottom: 0;}span.pt-0000015188cdab-23a4-4691-a0bf-08bd12ee47ce {font-family: Times New Roman;color: black;font-style: normal;font-weight: normal;margin: 0;padding: 0;}</style></p><p class="pt-0000003ca63d5b-061b-4f2b-abfc-451cf8847673" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml"><span class="math-tex" style="font-family: Cambria Math !important;" xmlns="">\(∴\frac{dy}{dx}{\left.​\right| }_{(2,2\sqrt{2})}=\frac{2}{2\sqrt{2}}=\frac{1}{\sqrt{2}}\) </span><span xml:space="preserve" class="pt-0000013ca63d5b-061b-4f2b-abfc-451cf8847673"> </span><style>span { white-space: pre-wrap; }p.pt-0000003ca63d5b-061b-4f2b-abfc-451cf8847673 {margin-left: 0.31in;margin-right: 0.25in;text-indent: -0.31in;text-align: left;line-height: 108%;margin-top: 0;margin-bottom: 0;}span.pt-0000013ca63d5b-061b-4f2b-abfc-451cf8847673 {font-family: Times New Roman;color: black;font-style: normal;font-weight: normal;margin: 0;padding: 0;}</style></p></span>
                                    </div>
                            </div>
                        </div>
                        <div class="row questionBlock">

                            <div class="row question">
                                <div class="col-md-12" style="padding-left:0px; padding-right:0px;">
                                    <div class="row">
                                        <div class="serial">
                                            <span>Question 90 </span>
                                        </div>
                                        <div class="questionText" style="display: block;">
                                            <p class="pt-0000004f4006de-1a95-401b-a38b-f072238ac313" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml"><span class="math-tex" style="font-family: Cambria Math !important;" xmlns="">\(\int \frac{dx}{{\left({e}^{x}+{e}^{-x}\right)}^{2}}=?\) </span><span xml:space="preserve" class="pt-0000014f4006de-1a95-401b-a38b-f072238ac313"><span>            </span> </span><span xml:space="preserve" class="pt-0000024f4006de-1a95-401b-a38b-f072238ac313"> </span><style>span { white-space: pre-wrap; }p.pt-0000004f4006de-1a95-401b-a38b-f072238ac313 {line-height: 108%;margin-top: 0;margin-left: 0;margin-right: 0;margin-bottom: 0;}span.pt-0000014f4006de-1a95-401b-a38b-f072238ac313 {font-family: SutonnyMJ;color: black;font-style: normal;font-weight: normal;margin: 0;padding: 0;}span.pt-0000024f4006de-1a95-401b-a38b-f072238ac313 {font-family: Times New Roman;color: black;font-style: normal;font-weight: normal;margin: 0;padding: 0;}</style></p>
                                        </div>
