                                </div>
                                    <div class="row solveText" style="display: block; padding:10px; color:#077307; overflow-x: auto; background-color: #d7f7d4;">
                                        <span style="color: black !important; font-weight: bold;">Solution:</span>
                                        <br />
                                        <span style="color: black !important;"><p class="pt-000000298ac645-d14b-4220-b37b-6b10e6d87155" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml"><span class="math-tex" style="font-family: Cambria Math !important;" xmlns="">\(Let,\ {e}^{2x}+1=z\ ⇒2{e}^{2x}dx=dz\) </span><span xml:space="preserve" class="pt-000001298ac645-d14b-4220-b37b-6b10e6d87155"> ;</span><style>span { white-space: pre-wrap; }p.pt-000000298ac645-d14b-4220-b37b-6b10e6d87155 {line-height: 108%;margin-top: 0;margin-left: 0;margin-right: 0;margin-bottom: 0;}span.pt-000001298ac645-d14b-4220-b37b-6b10e6d87155 {font-family: Times New Roman;color: black;font-style: normal;font-weight: normal;margin: 0;padding: 0;}</style></p><p class="pt-00000001bfca9c-b4fb-4891-b358-3a6e8d16e3a8" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml"><span class="math-tex" style="font-family: Cambria Math !important;" xmlns="">\(\int \frac{dx}{{\left({e}^{x}+{e}^{-x}\right)}^{2}}=\frac{1}{2}\int \frac{2{e}^{2x}dx}{{\left({e}^{2x}+1\right)}^{2}}=\frac{1}{2}\int \frac{dz}{{z}^{2}}=-\frac{1}{2}\ .\frac{1}{z}+c=\frac{-1}{2\left({e}^{2x}+1\right)}+c\) </span><span xml:space="preserve" class="pt-00000101bfca9c-b4fb-4891-b358-3a6e8d16e3a8"> </span><style>span { white-space: pre-wrap; }p.pt-00000001bfca9c-b4fb-4891-b358-3a6e8d16e3a8 {line-height: 108%;margin-top: 0;margin-left: 0;margin-right: 0;margin-bottom: 0;}span.pt-00000101bfca9c-b4fb-4891-b358-3a6e8d16e3a8 {font-family: Times New Roman;color: black;font-style: normal;font-weight: normal;margin: 0;padding: 0;}</style></p></span>
                                    </div>
                            </div>
                        </div>
                        <div class="row questionBlock">

                            <div class="row question">
                                <div class="col-md-12" style="padding-left:0px; padding-right:0px;">
                                    <div class="row">
                                        <div class="serial">
                                            <span>Question 91 </span>
                                        </div>
                                        <div class="questionText" style="display: block;">
                                            <p class="pt-000000d00fdb36-e05d-45e5-bcc1-7993fb55c6de" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml"><span class="math-tex" style="font-family: Cambria Math !important;" xmlns="">\(y={x}^{2},\ x=1,\ x=3\) </span><span xml:space="preserve" class="pt-000001d00fdb36-e05d-45e5-bcc1-7993fb55c6de"> </span><span xml:space="preserve" class="pt-000002d00fdb36-e05d-45e5-bcc1-7993fb55c6de">Ges </span><span class="pt-000001d00fdb36-e05d-45e5-bcc1-7993fb55c6de">x</span><span class="pt-000002d00fdb36-e05d-45e5-bcc1-7993fb55c6de">-</span><span class="pt-000002d00fdb36-e05d-45e5-bcc1-7993fb55c6de">A&#255;</span><span xml:space="preserve" class="pt-000002d00fdb36-e05d-45e5-bcc1-7993fb55c6de"> </span><span class="pt-000002d00fdb36-e05d-45e5-bcc1-7993fb55c6de">&#216;viv</span><span xml:space="preserve" class="pt-000002d00fdb36-e05d-45e5-bcc1-7993fb55c6de"> </span><span class="pt-000002d00fdb36-e05d-45e5-bcc1-7993fb55c6de">mxgve</span><span class="pt-000002d00fdb36-e05d-45e5-bcc1-7993fb55c6de">&#215; †</span><span class="pt-000002d00fdb36-e05d-45e5-bcc1-7993fb55c6de">&#255;‡&#206;i</span><span xml:space="preserve" class="pt-000002d00fdb36-e05d-45e5-bcc1-7993fb55c6de"> †</span><span class="pt-000002d00fdb36-e05d-45e5-bcc1-7993fb55c6de">&#255;&#206;dj</span><span class="pt-000002d00fdb36-e05d-45e5-bcc1-7993fb55c6de">-</span><span xml:space="preserve" class="pt-000001d00fdb36-e05d-45e5-bcc1-7993fb55c6de"><span>            </span> </span><style>span { white-space: pre-wrap; }p.pt-000000d00fdb36-e05d-45e5-bcc1-7993fb55c6de {line-height: 108%;margin-top: 0;margin-left: 0;margin-right: 0;margin-bottom: 0;}span.pt-000001d00fdb36-e05d-45e5-bcc1-7993fb55c6de {font-family: Times New Roman;color: black;font-style: normal;font-weight: normal;margin: 0;padding: 0;}span.pt-000002d00fdb36-e05d-45e5-bcc1-7993fb55c6de {font-family: SutonnyMJ;color: black;font-style: normal;font-weight: normal;margin: 0;padding: 0;}</style></p>
                                        </div>
                                    </div>
