                                    <div class="row solveText" style="display: block; padding:10px; color:#077307; overflow-x: auto; background-color: #d7f7d4;">
                                        <span style="color: black !important; font-weight: bold;">Solution:</span>
                                        <br />
                                        <span style="color: black !important;"><p class="pt-000000d2d36c95-c580-4fa9-8814-15b39b46f64c" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml"><span class="pt-000001d2d36c95-c580-4fa9-8814-15b39b46f64c"><img src="data:image/png;base64," style="width: 0.8116885in;height: 0.5662948in;" alt="Picture 6" /></span><span xml:space="preserve" class="pt-000002d2d36c95-c580-4fa9-8814-15b39b46f64c"> </span><style>span { white-space: pre-wrap; }p.pt-000000d2d36c95-c580-4fa9-8814-15b39b46f64c {line-height: 108%;margin-top: 0;margin-left: 0;margin-right: 0;margin-bottom: 0;}span.pt-000001d2d36c95-c580-4fa9-8814-15b39b46f64c {color: black;font-style: normal;font-weight: normal;margin: 0;padding: 0;}span.pt-000002d2d36c95-c580-4fa9-8814-15b39b46f64c {font-family: Times New Roman;color: black;font-style: normal;font-weight: normal;margin: 0;padding: 0;}</style></p><p class="pt-000000407e63d7-eae1-42c7-9fd7-7f8cb703d0e1" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml"><span class="math-tex" style="font-family: Cambria Math !important;" xmlns="">\(A=\ \int_{1}^{3} {x}^{2}dx={\left(\frac{{x}^{3}}{3}\right)}_{1}^{3}=\frac{27}{3}-\frac{1}{3}=\frac{26}{3}\) </span><span xml:space="preserve" class="pt-000001407e63d7-eae1-42c7-9fd7-7f8cb703d0e1">  </span><style>span { white-space: pre-wrap; }p.pt-000000407e63d7-eae1-42c7-9fd7-7f8cb703d0e1 {line-height: 108%;margin-top: 0;margin-left: 0;margin-right: 0;margin-bottom: 0;}span.pt-000001407e63d7-eae1-42c7-9fd7-7f8cb703d0e1 {font-family: Times New Roman;color: black;font-style: normal;font-weight: normal;margin: 0;padding: 0;}</style></p></span>
                                    </div>
