                                        <span style="color: black !important;"><p class="pt-000000ae73bcf2-228d-4caf-82b4-9f7fa3fc91b4" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml"><span class="math-tex" style="font-family: Cambria Math !important;" xmlns="">\(5\left({x}^{2}+2.\frac{3}{2}.x+\frac{9}{4}\right)=10y+4+\frac{45}{4}\) </span><span xml:space="preserve" class="pt-000001ae73bcf2-228d-4caf-82b4-9f7fa3fc91b4"> </span><style>span { white-space: pre-wrap; }p.pt-000000ae73bcf2-228d-4caf-82b4-9f7fa3fc91b4 {line-height: 108%;margin-top: 0;margin-left: 0;margin-right: 0;margin-bottom: 0;}span.pt-000001ae73bcf2-228d-4caf-82b4-9f7fa3fc91b4 {font-family: SolaimanLipi;color: black;font-style: normal;font-weight: normal;margin: 0;padding: 0;}</style></p><p class="pt-0000002a14e909-1115-4e08-8630-721b7f4bddfc" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml"><span class="math-tex" style="font-family: Cambria Math !important;" xmlns="">\(⇒{\left(x+\frac{3}{2}\right)}^{2}=\frac{10}{5}\left(y+\frac{61}{40}\right)∴{X}^{2}=2Y\ ∴a=\frac{1}{2}\ \) </span><span xml:space="preserve" class="pt-0000012a14e909-1115-4e08-8630-721b7f4bddfc"> </span><style>span { white-space: pre-wrap; }p.pt-0000002a14e909-1115-4e08-8630-721b7f4bddfc {line-height: 108%;margin-top: 0;margin-left: 0;margin-right: 0;margin-bottom: 0;}span.pt-0000012a14e909-1115-4e08-8630-721b7f4bddfc {font-family: SolaimanLipi;color: black;font-style: normal;font-weight: normal;margin: 0;padding: 0;}</style></p><p class="pt-000000cb13d408-e0c2-4f18-8186-c84e7274f503" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml"><span class="math-tex" style="font-family: Cambria Math !important;" xmlns="">\(∴Y+\frac{1}{2}=0⇒y+\frac{61}{40}+\frac{1}{2}=0\) </span><span xml:space="preserve" class="pt-000001cb13d408-e0c2-4f18-8186-c84e7274f503"> </span><style>span { white-space: pre-wrap; }p.pt-000000cb13d408-e0c2-4f18-8186-c84e7274f503 {line-height: 108%;margin-top: 0;margin-left: 0;margin-right: 0;margin-bottom: 0;}span.pt-000001cb13d408-e0c2-4f18-8186-c84e7274f503 {f